#, no-c-format
msgid "Mk.6:13 And they were...anointing with oil many sick people and healing them."
msgstr "Mar.6:13 En zij [...] zalfden vele zieken met olie en genazen hen."

#. Tag: listitem
#: how2-interpretation.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
